            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dayasadan Agarwal Vidyalaya School (DSAV) is doing a great job to provide better and affordable education to the students which they all wanted.This is the school where our students get proper education so that our country could develop in all possible way. The significance of this school is that they provide all the knowledge related to sports, education, moral value, etc. The teachers, staff and other members of this school are honest at their works.The academic result of this school has been great for many years.This shows how good the teachers of this school is! This school provides better facilities for the students. The fee of this school is very much affordable for the students’ parents. From my point of view this is one of the best schools in Chennai which has been serving our nation in the field of education for many years.",
