            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dayasadan Agarwal Vidyala is a very good school. They provide excellent education and all the teachers gives individual attention to each and every child right from KG to class XII. The infrastructure is good and all the class rooms are equipped well maintained.Children enjoy going to school as there are so many extra curricular activities, talents ect...... Fee structure is also reasonable when compared to other reputed schools.\n\nDefinitely i would recommend this school for those who expect their kids to have holistic development!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
