            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent, I am very much pleased.  Very good infrastructure and caring teachers, timely appreciation for the students, Encouraging students to participate in extra curricular activities like bull bull, chess, skating and inter school competition.\nProviding constructive feedback during the parents meeting that indicates the transparency.\nI must thank for the all the teaching staff for their commitment.\nFinally  very safe place for students.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
