            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I take this opportunity to thank the principal mam, teachers and management for providing excellent education to the students. Besides studies, co-curricular activities are also given equal importance which helps in grooming the skills of my kids and all other students. Teachers are so friendly and guiding the students to participate in all the activities.\nI wish all the very best to the institution for their bright future ahead.",
          "publisher": {
